{"tid":2323580,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外媒關注《許願》原型強姦犯出獄 趙斗淳引逾百YouTuber聚集為鄰居帶來滋擾","createTime":"2020-12-13T09:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T12:45:41.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f4cdab3f684fafb506b9f0b7dd1d9adcf8a2d0","tid":2323580,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:25:51.000Z","msg":"令居民冇覺好瞓<br />\n另外，趙斗淳屬於惡名昭彰的性罪犯，所以有YouTuber及網民都自發性到其家附近聚集進行抗議，同時又暗示會對他進行私刑。當中連日來都有不少YouTuber在趙斗淳居所前開直播同叫囂。根據今日韓媒報道，自從趙斗淳昨日出獄後，有不少人在安山市其居所附近聚集，今早有10多人在趙斗淳居所前大叫：「食得落早餐嗎？」由於持續的騷擾，令趙斗淳的鄰居亦大受困擾，更紛紛報警求助。當中鄰居A某受訪時就憤怒地說：「因為YouTuber主播們晚上睡不着覺，就拿着相機在外面整夜用髒話大喊，每條小巷都有人在吸煙，冇得好好睡一覺。趙斗淳回來已令人心煩死了，連圍觀的人也來吵吵鬧鬧，這樣怎能活下去呢？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201213/GYYZXX6ZSJAIRO26CKW5OVJVRY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201213%2FGYYZXX6ZSJAIRO26CKW5OVJVRY%2F&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mbhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=327a15f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201213%2FGYYZXX6ZSJAIRO26CKW5OVJVRY%2F&h=0c6970b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201213/GYYZXX6ZSJAIRO26CKW5OVJVRY/</a>"},{"pid":"0d84d3c18be3ba83c49f6170e7d684fc9783a33d","tid":2323580,"uid":112081,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:27:55.000Z","msg":"啲鄰居唔驚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73dd5eee4497eccfe5717f7625f035f1c5aaddb7","tid":2323580,"uid":247905,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:28:01.000Z","msg":"就算無人示威<br />\nD鄰居會住得安心咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb1977816e4473801f33e1264714ded97ea84da","tid":2323580,"uid":284432,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:28:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0f6c3bc4a7665e81c50bb5d1baeb99650b80ce6","tid":2323580,"uid":2